Saya mahukan perhatian penuh awak.

848
00:54:07,749 --> 00:54:08,583
Hanya saya.

849
00:54:08,583 --> 00:54:09,751
awak sangat kelakar.

850
00:54:12,087 --> 00:54:13,380
awak sangat hodoh!

